What are Drones for Pipeline Inspection?
These drones combine aeronautical engineering with advanced sensing payloads to create a mobile inspection laboratory. Fixed‑wing variants deliver long‑range endurance for thousands of kilometres of on‑shore corridor, while multi‑rotor units provide precision hover capabilities for offshore valve stations and subsea tie‑backs. Integrated AI analytics can automatically flag corrosion hotspots, vegetation growth, or third‑party interference, turning raw imagery into actionable intelligence without extensive post‑flight processing.
